{"Author": "William Irizarry", "Date": "on April 27, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "great product", "Text": "great product. works flawless with alexa"}
{"Author": "drkraver", "Date": "on April 27, 2018", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Leaks suck no matter what", "Text": "it's okay, not sure if it is worth it. By the time you get the alert the water has already done damage. Leaks suck no matter what."}
