{"Author": "JR", "Date": "on April 15, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "it seems to be working and all is good for now", "Text": "I bought this as a warehouse deal and it was missing the power supply. Other than having to learn how to do a factory reset and find the welcome code to set it up, it seems to be working and all is good for now."}
{"Author": "Keith", "Date": "on April 14, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Apple App Unusable", "Text": "I can not recommend this product. As of April 2018 the Apple App is so bad the product is unusable. Check the App reviews prior to purchase.\n\nSo much potential, I hope they get it worked out."}
{"Author": "Patrick Anderson", "Date": "on April 12, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "If you want a side job of constantly readding devices, this is for you", "Text": "Devices keep dropping. Have to reset to bring them back. Resetting several devices regularly is painful. Each device has different instructions and often not found again. Support responds 3+ days to tell you to reset. #worthless"}
