{"Author": "Amazon Customer", "Date": "on April 11, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Does a fantastic job controlling our smart switches", "Text": "Does a fantastic job controlling our smart switches, plugs, smart thermostat, garage door, and door lock. It also plays well with Alexa. The app has been very useful, and I've found a couple of essential add-ons through the SmartThings website."}
{"Author": "Tammy Sherrill", "Date": "on April 10, 2018", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Smart home necessity", "Text": "Love that we are able to tie all of our SMART products into one application."}
{"Author": "Buk", "Date": "on April 10, 2018", "Stars": "5.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Connects easily to our wired network and provides wireless signal throughout ...", "Text": "Samsung seems to be supporting version two with updates to firmware. Connects easily to our wired network and provides wireless signal throughout our single story wood framed house and basement."}
