{"Author": "Eric J Urbaniec", "Date": "on January 22, 2018", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "And Alexa is useless unless you want to play game", "Text": "No manual on how it works. Need to go on line and search but 9 times out of 10 gives no solution. When set up to recognize I\u2019m back doesn\u2019t work. Things are 50/50 on working. Setting them up frustrating. And Alexa is useless unless you want to play game. For security look elsewhere."}
{"Author": "Mr. J", "Date": "on January 22, 2018", "Stars": "2.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "The product loves to die just outside warranty, so ...", "Text": "The product loves to die just outside warranty, so plan on spending $100 every 13 to 28 months.\nWhen working it does okay.\nWill probably lower rating to one star if the replacement requires setting up everything from scratch."}
