{"Author": "gender8ombs", "Date": "on October 23, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "I dig it. A welcome addition to my smart home ecosystem.", "Text": "Works with harmony, Google Home, wemo, and Phillips hue. Kind of links a few things together that I really needed to link. The set of sensors are reliable and easy as pie to set up, and Samsung has a ton of free programs to utilize these sensors, like for the elderly, you can get an alert if there is no motion detected after some time, and there's even a service for home monitoring and security. My motion sensor turns on my kitchen lights, it really impresses the guests :)"}
