{"Author": "Parm", "Date": "on October 21, 2017", "Stars": "4.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "works good, could be better", "Text": "works good, could be better, lots more possibilities with the software,\n\nwish it supported a countdown feature, like after x min this will happen after something is turned off or on."}
