{"Author": "Terry Beatty", "Date": "on August 13, 2017", "Stars": "1.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Not as advertised", "Text": "Piece of white JUNK. If you are looking for something to work on, and spend hrs of frustration then buy this. If you are looking for something to work with, this isn't for you. Thing won't pair with devices as claimed. Your \"things\" show up \"offline\" for no reason. The thing is completely unreliable just for turning off/on lights much less anything else. I regret my purchase and it gives me strong doubts about future samsung electronics"}
