{"Author": "Paul Watanabe", "Date": "on August 6, 2017", "Stars": "3.0 out of 5 stars", "Title": "Was fairly easy to go with", "Text": "Occasionally loses connection or has to be reset. Works with everything that it should, no compatibility issues. Was fairly easy to go with. App is super clunky and full of more bugs than a picnic at the park. Gets stuck in this endless loop of having to login over and over again, won't keep you logged in, makes the app and gear completely useless at times. They could learn a thing or two from Lutron and Belkin, whose apps have worked flawlessly for me."}
